import { Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import { Box } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'

export const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <Box sx={{height: "30vh", backgroundColor: "#000", color: "#fff" }}>
        <Grid container spacing={3}>
            <Grid item>
                <Typography>Acerca de Nosotros</Typography>
                <Box>
                    <Typography>Quiénes somos</Typography>
                    <Typography>Sala de prensa</Typography>
                    <Typography>Sostenibilidad</Typography>

                </Box>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item>
                <Typography>Información legal</Typography>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item>
                <Typography>Explorar</Typography>

                <Typography>Prepara tu viaje</Typography>
                <Typography>Destinos</Typography>
                
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    </Box>
  )
}
